<div style="text-align:justify;"><strong><span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:7pt;">1. &#160;</span>&#160; <span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:7pt;">&#160;Copyright Assignment</span></strong></div>
